Redirecting dmesg to an USB device if the Android is not showing up detailed loglevel. Can also redirect logcat to an USB.

init.rc file
on early-boot
#mkdir /mnt/usb
mount /dev/(usb_stick) /mnt/usb
exec /system/bin/dmesg >  /mnt/usb/dmesg.log
exec /system/bin/logcat > /mnt/usb/logcat.log

Kernel Config:
CONFIG_VT_CONSOLE=y
CONFIG_TTY=y
CONFIG_VT=y
